{"tid":737591,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[7月新番]Angolmois元寇合戰記","createTime":"2018-07-11T03:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T12:40:06.000Z","uid":50124,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"89a58ea057b1052acbc621076226bac63882ca15","tid":737591,"uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:08:44.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇?港澳台正版俾B站買左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蒙古軍席捲了中世紀歐洲，傳說「恐怖的大王」＝「Angolmois」就是源自他們。1274 年，他們來到了日本，在前往博多的對馬島上，出現了被流放的罪犯&mdash;&mdash;鎌倉武士朽井迅三郎，他將在這裡與蒙古軍展開對峙！<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n原作：たかぎ七彦<br />\n監督：栗山貴行<br />\n助監督：羽原久美子<br />\nシリーズ構成：ヤスカワショウゴ<br />\nキャラクターデザイン・総作画監督：小峰正頼<br />\nアニメーション制作：NAZ<br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n朽井迅三郎：小野友樹<br />\n輝日：Lynn<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RE2hsJa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRE2hsJa.jpg&h=a4460ac1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1067a059926ba5a9af996ada1e7a72a1f2464802","tid":737591,"uid":8867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:10:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7609d0aa65bf5c89336534aeb37753902fb27ed","tid":737591,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:10:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb5695d44f5ba19751d99e9cb5dc62283894382f","tid":737591,"uid":39840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:39:24.000Z","msg":"睇動畫入面既人佔大部份既萌豚對哩套冇興趣<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 生肉單行本追到最新一期"},{"pid":"1079487cfa474622bf5519f2fba9fd60442ba1f4","tid":737591,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"幾好睇,但有啲位音效做得好,反而作畫表現唔到相應既魄力"},{"pid":"0088244394e1b9100f11f2e254f58d8d2820c465","tid":737591,"uid":60909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T15:34:14.000Z","msg":"個feel幾似四月番套黃金神威，幾正"},{"pid":"ac36ebdf4a141f937d6d48980473cb98c7ff61fb","tid":737591,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T15:36:31.000Z","msg":